{
  "text": "The minimal increase in CRA values, provide improved easy care properties. Figure 4b shows an increase in CRA as compare to untreated sample the reason behind that the PLA-CS nanocomposite fills the amorphous regions and causes to improve the CRA [CITATION_1] . Figure 4c shows that after the application with PLA-CS nanocomposite, the tensile strength of the treated fabric improved on increasing the nanocomposite contents (1-3% w/v). The overall increment as compare to control fabric is due to the binding of PLA nanocomposite between fiber and yarn [CITATION_2] .",
